\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

I would have been pleased to meet you, had we been acquainted under different
 circumstances.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

I cannot make the same assumption.
 Now, move,
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 said Sustar with a sigh and a slight shove.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

It does not suit you at all, Saul.
 But then again, perhaps it does,
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 said Philetus and shrugged ever so slightly.
 Sustar raised a pointed finger and said irately:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

One more word until the Tribunal addresses you and I'll use that batton
