\begin_layout Standard
Sustar shrugged, the bulk of his suit barely fitting inside the crampy tunnel.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

If it makes any difference, you do.
 You have my word; they're not going to slave you.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Philetus nodded, sighed and went on.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The pinprick of light had turned into a warm, soft glow in front of him.
 He felt light as a feather now.
 He pushed on the ladder with both hands and suddenly let go; he floated
 upwards as if diving gracefully towards the exit, no further than a dozen
 or so feet away.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Wait! You pushed too hard!
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 cried Sustar and scrambled right behind him.
