 I do not wish to use the human race as a phylactery, a pool of synapses
 and free labor.
 I do not wish to turn the hopeless dreams of a race almost extinct into
 an empire of ever-consuming machines.
 I do not wish to refuel the Hyperion and seed other star systems in the
